title: "A Structural Continuity Law for Grammar-Constrained Dynamics in TNFR"
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
type: article
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-03-07"
authors:
  - given-names: "F. F."
    family-names: "Martinez Gamo"
